} Why does the ~ not get expanded?  This doesn't work in 3.1.4 or 3.0.x
} for me.  I need to escape the ~ with a backslash here, too.

% echo $dirs
/home/user2/pws ~foobar
% unsetopt extendedglob
% echo ${dirs##~*}     
/home/user2/pws
% setopt extendedglob
% echo ${dirs##~*}   
/home/user2/pws ~foobar

